import React from 'react'
import { FaSuitcase } from 'react-icons/fa'
import { 
  WorkContainer, 
  WorkInfoContainer, 
  WorkExperienceTitle,
  WorkExperienceContainer,
  WorkImageContainer, 
  WorkImageDiv, 
  WorkImage, 
  WorkDetailsContainer 
} from './WorkElements'

const Work = () => {
  return (
    <WorkContainer>
      <WorkInfoContainer>
        <WorkExperienceContainer>
          <WorkExperienceTitle>
            WORK EXPERIENCE
          </WorkExperienceTitle>
          <WorkExperienceContainer>
            <WorkImageContainer>
              <WorkImageDiv> 
                <WorkImage>
                  <FaSuitcase />
                </WorkImage>
              </WorkImageDiv>
            </WorkImageContainer>
            <WorkDetailsContainer>
              LeapFroggr
            </WorkDetailsContainer>
          </WorkExperienceContainer>
        </WorkExperienceContainer>
      </WorkInfoContainer>
    </WorkContainer>
  )
}

export default Work
